{
  "id": "adv_card_mku_02_03",
  "title": "初音ミク 3話 夏はまたやってくる！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "うう……すっかり遊ぶことが目的になって\n自由研究のことを忘れていましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（On Miku's suggestion‚ we decided to spend our last day in Hokkaido sightseeing in Hakodate）\n（We toured the streets and facilities with many attractions——）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "正直そんなことだろうとは思ってたよ\n琴乃もそう思うだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Goryokaku was impressive. It really has\na beautiful star shape. I was genuinely moved",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.7354418913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、えっと……\n私は一緒に遊んでしまったので……反省してます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more you learn about it‚ the more interesting this building is\nDuring the Battle of Hakodate‚ it functioned as the headquarters of the former shogunate army——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.9459636528
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　もう！！　{user}さん！！\n気付いていたのなら教えてくださいまし！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The place where Toshizo Hijikata‚ the demon vice―commander of the Shinsengumi‚ finally arrived\nAfter that‚ he fought on the front lines until the very end…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "もうヘトヘトで、とても気力なんてわきませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you a fan of the Shinsengumi?\nWow‚ you know a lot of details",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9848062992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……ちょっと残念\n私はまだまだ遊び足りないぐらいだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather‚ I respect leaders throughout history\nNot just the Shinsengumi‚ but both domestic and foreign ones",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.5666694641
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんの自由研究のテーマ探し\nお手伝い出来るかなって思ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I'm the leader of LizNoir too\nThere must be a lot to learn. That's why I researched various things",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.538374567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、ミク\nお気持ちだけ、受け取っておきますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so as you were researching\nYou ended up becoming knowledgeable about history too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.9450413386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、ミクは凄いですわね\n全然疲れていない様子ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Rio‚ did you drop something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.4764473278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "今日だって、複数公演の合間でしょう？\n体を休めたりしなくて大丈夫だった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "平気だよ\nみんなとこうして遊ぶ方がいい思い出になるから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ could it be that the knowledge you just shared…\nThis is… a tourist pamphlet for the Goryokaku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.833317566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.2203117847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。きっとそのバイタリティーこそ、ミクが\n歌で世界中の人々を魅了している秘訣なのでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S―shouldn't we go into a store soon!?\nI'm starting to get hungry too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.3942802588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4の私達ですら、まだまだ難しいこと……\nそれこそ、ミクをもっとよく知れば私達も……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She dodged the question. Rio seems unusually excited）\n（Seeing a different side of her is also a pleasure unique to traveling）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.0864111106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ！\nミクを研究テーマにすればいいんですのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}!\nWhat's with that lukewarm look!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6451864243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
