      "text": "全然OKだよ、私は大歓迎！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Beautiful…\nSo this is the famous night view of Hakodate",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
