      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_02_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ミク……！　ありがとうですわ！\nそういうことなら、もう一度海に行きますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I understand why they say\nyou must see this when you come to Hakodate",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2666554769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
